This paper deals with natural language processing and deep learning techniques to extract relevant information from financial news articles. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval and machine learning, which are relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses unsupervised learning techniques, which are relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with financial risk analytics, which could be relevant to cs.CY (Cryptography and Security).
